{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2 id=\"splash-screen\"><a href=\"#splash-screen\" aria-label=\"splash screen permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Splash screen</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/flame-engine/flame_splash_screen/master/demogif.gif\"></p>\n<p>Style your flame game with a beautiful splash screen.</p>\n<p>Flame splash screen is a very customizable splash screen package. </p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"dart\"><pre class=\"language-dart\"><code class=\"language-dart\"><span class=\"token function\">FlameSplashScreen</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n  theme<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> FlameSplashTheme<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>dark<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  onFinish<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>BuildContext context<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> Navigator<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">pushNamed</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>context<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'/your-game-initial-screen'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Check the <a href=\"https://github.com/flame-engine/flame_splash_screen\">package's repo</a> and the <a href=\"https://pub.dev/